{
  "sourceLanguage": "en",
  "strings": {
    "": {},
    "\"\"                 Unable to connect to the AI enhancement service.                                  Please check:                 1. Your internet connection                 2. The API endpoint URL is correct                 3. The service is not experiencing an outage                                  The transcription was saved without enhancement.                 \"\"": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"                 Verbindung zum KI-Verbesserungsdienst nicht möglich.                                  Bitte prüfen Sie:                 1. Ihre Internetverbindung                 2. Die API-Endpunkt-URL ist korrekt                 3. Der Dienst hat keine Störung                                  Die Transkription wurde ohne Verbesserung gespeichert.                 \"\""
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"                 Unable to connect to the AI enhancement service.                                  Please check:                 1. Your internet connection                 2. The API endpoint URL is correct                 3. The service is not experiencing an outage                                  The transcription was saved without enhancement.                 \"\""
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"                 Unable to connect to the AI enhancement service.                                  Please check:                 1. Your internet connection                 2. The API endpoint URL is correct                 3. The service is not experiencing an outage                                  The transcription was saved without enhancement.                 \"\""
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"                 Impossible de se connecter au service d'amélioration IA.                                  Veuillez vérifier :                 1. Votre connexion internet                 2. L'URL du point de terminaison API est correcte                 3. Le service ne subit pas de panne                                  La transcription a été enregistrée sans amélioration.                 \"\""
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\" AI 拡張サービスに接続できません。                                  以下を確認してください。 1. インターネット接続 2. API エンドポイント URL が正しい 3. サービスが停止していない 文字起こしは拡張せずに保存されました。                 「」"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"                 无法连接到 AI 增强服务。                                  请检查：                 1. 您的互联网连接                 2. API 端点 URL 是否正确                 3. 服务是否正常运行                                  转录已保存，未进行增强。                 \"\""
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\" Não é possível conectar-se ao serviço de aprimoramento de IA.                                  Verifique: 1. Sua conexão com a Internet 2. O URL do terminal da API está correto 3. O serviço não está sofrendo uma interrupção A transcrição foi salva sem melhorias.                 \"\""
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\" Impossibile connettersi al servizio di miglioramento dell'intelligenza artificiale.                                  Controlla: 1. La tua connessione Internet 2. L'URL dell'endpoint API è corretto 3. Il servizio non presenta un'interruzione La trascrizione è stata salvata senza miglioramenti.                 \"\""
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "\"\"                 You've exceeded your API rate limit or quota.                                  To fix this:                 1. Wait a few minutes and try again                 2. Check your API provider's usage limits                 3. Consider upgrading your API plan                                  The transcription was saved without enhancement.                 \"\"": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"                 Sie haben Ihr API-Ratenlimit oder Kontingent überschritten.                                  So beheben Sie das:                 1. Warten Sie einige Minuten und versuchen Sie es erneut                 2. Prüfen Sie die Nutzungslimits Ihres API-Anbieters                 3. Erwägen Sie ein Upgrade Ihres API-Plans                                  Die Transkription wurde ohne Verbesserung gespeichert.                 \"\""
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"                 You've exceeded your API rate limit or quota.                                  To fix this:                 1. Wait a few minutes and try again                 2. Check your API provider's usage limits                 3. Consider upgrading your API plan                                  The transcription was saved without enhancement.                 \"\""
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"                 You've exceeded your API rate limit or quota.                                  To fix this:                 1. Wait a few minutes and try again                 2. Check your API provider's usage limits                 3. Consider upgrading your API plan                                  The transcription was saved without enhancement.                 \"\""
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"                 Vous avez dépassé votre limite de taux ou quota API.                                  Pour corriger cela :                 1. Attendez quelques minutes et réessayez                 2. Vérifiez les limites d'utilisation de votre fournisseur API                 3. Envisagez de mettre à niveau votre plan API                                  La transcription a été enregistrée sans amélioration.                 \"\""
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\" API レート制限または割り当てを超過しました。                                  これを修正するには: 1. 数分待ってから再試行します。 2. API プロバイダーの使用制限を確認します。 3. API プランのアップグレードを検討してください。 文字起こしは拡張せずに保存されました。                 「」"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"                 您已超出 API 速率限制或配额。                                  解决方法：                 1. 等待几分钟后重试                 2. 检查您的 API 提供商的使用限制                 3. 考虑升级您的 API 计划                                  转录已保存，未进行增强。                 \"\""
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\" Você excedeu seu limite ou cota de taxa de API.                                  Para corrigir isso: 1. Aguarde alguns minutos e tente novamente 2. Verifique os limites de uso do seu provedor de API 3. Considere atualizar seu plano de API A transcrição foi salva sem melhorias.                 \"\""
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\" Hai superato il limite di velocità o la quota API.                                  Per risolvere questo problema: 1. Attendi qualche minuto e riprova 2. Controlla i limiti di utilizzo del tuo provider API 3. Valuta la possibilità di aggiornare il tuo piano API La trascrizione è stata salvata senza miglioramenti.                 \"\""
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "\"\"                 Your API key appears to be invalid or expired.                                  To fix this:                 1. Open Settings → AI Enhancement                 2. Verify your API key is correct                 3. Check that your API endpoint is correct                                  The transcription was saved without enhancement.                 \"\"": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"                 Ihr API-Schlüssel scheint ungültig oder abgelaufen zu sein.                                  So beheben Sie das:                 1. Öffnen Sie Einstellungen → KI-Verbesserung                 2. Überprüfen Sie, ob Ihr API-Schlüssel korrekt ist                 3. Prüfen Sie, ob Ihr API-Endpunkt korrekt ist                                  Die Transkription wurde ohne Verbesserung gespeichert.                 \"\""
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"                 Your API key appears to be invalid or expired.                                  To fix this:                 1. Open Settings → AI Enhancement                 2. Verify your API key is correct                 3. Check that your API endpoint is correct                                  The transcription was saved without enhancement.                 \"\""
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"                 Your API key appears to be invalid or expired.                                  To fix this:                 1. Open Settings → AI Enhancement                 2. Verify your API key is correct                 3. Check that your API endpoint is correct                                  The transcription was saved without enhancement.                 \"\""
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"                 Votre clé API semble invalide ou expirée.                                  Pour corriger cela :                 1. Ouvrez Paramètres → Amélioration IA                 2. Vérifiez que votre clé API est correcte                 3. Vérifiez que votre point de terminaison API est correct                                  La transcription a été enregistrée sans amélioration.                 \"\""
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\" API キーが無効か期限切れのようです。                                  これを修正するには: 1. [設定] → [AI 拡張] を開きます。 2. API キーが正しいことを確認します。 3. API エンドポイントが正しいことを確認します。 文字起こしは拡張なしで保存されました。                 「」"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"                 您的 API 密钥似乎无效或已过期。                                  解决方法：                 1. 打开设置 → AI 增强                 2. 验证您的 API 密钥是否正确                 3. 检查您的 API 端点是否正确                                  转录已保存，未进行增强。                 \"\""
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\" Sua chave de API parece ser inválida ou expirou.                                  Para corrigir isso: 1. Abra Configurações → Aprimoramento de IA 2. Verifique se sua chave de API está correta 3. Verifique se seu endpoint de API está correto A transcrição foi salva sem aprimoramento.                 \"\""
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\" La tua chiave API sembra non essere valida o scaduta.                                  Per risolvere questo problema: 1. Apri Impostazioni → Miglioramento AI 2. Verifica che la chiave API sia corretta 3. Verifica che l'endpoint API sia corretto La trascrizione è stata salvata senza miglioramenti.                 \"\""
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "\"\"             Pindrop needs Accessibility permission to insert text at your cursor.                          To grant permission:             1. Click \"Open System Settings\" below             2. Click the + button             3. Navigate to the app shown in Finder             4. Restart Pindrop after granting permission                          Without this permission, text will only be copied to your clipboard.             \"\"": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"             Pindrop benötigt die Bedienungshilfen-Berechtigung, um Text an Ihrem Cursor einzufügen.                          So erteilen Sie die Berechtigung:             1. Klicken Sie unten auf \"Systemeinstellungen öffnen\"             2. Klicken Sie auf die + Schaltfläche             3. Navigieren Sie zur im Finder angezeigten App             4. Starten Sie Pindrop nach Erteilung der Berechtigung neu                          Ohne diese Berechtigung wird Text nur in Ihre Zwischenablage kopiert.             \"\""
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"             Pindrop needs Accessibility permission to insert text at your cursor.                          To grant permission:             1. Click \"Open System Settings\" below             2. Click the + button             3. Navigate to the app shown in Finder             4. Restart Pindrop after granting permission                          Without this permission, text will only be copied to your clipboard.             \"\""
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"             Pindrop needs Accessibility permission to insert text at your cursor.                          To grant permission:             1. Click \"Open System Settings\" below             2. Click the + button             3. Navigate to the app shown in Finder             4. Restart Pindrop after granting permission                          Without this permission, text will only be copied to your clipboard.             \"\""
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"             Pindrop a besoin de l'autorisation d'accessibilité pour insérer du texte à votre curseur.                          Pour accorder l'autorisation :             1. Cliquez sur \"Ouvrir les Paramètres Système\" ci-dessous             2. Cliquez sur le bouton +             3. Naviguez vers l'app affichée dans Finder             4. Redémarrez Pindrop après avoir accordé l'autorisation                          Sans cette autorisation, le texte sera uniquement copié dans votre presse-papiers.             \"\""
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\" Pindrop では、カーソル位置にテキストを挿入するにはアクセシビリティ権限が必要です。                          権限を付与するには: 1. 下の「システム設定を開く」をクリックします。 2. + ボタンをクリックします。 3. Finder に表示されているアプリに移動します。 4. 権限を付与した後、Pindrop を再起動します。 この権限がないと、テキストはクリップボードにコピーされるだけです。             「」"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"             Pindrop 需要辅助功能权限才能在您的光标处插入文本。                          授予权限：             1. 点击下方\"打开系统设置\"             2. 点击 + 按钮             3. 导航到 Finder 中显示的应用             4. 授予权限后重新启动 Pindrop                          没有此权限，文本将只复制到您的剪贴板。             \"\""
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\" Pindrop precisa de permissão de acessibilidade para inserir texto no cursor.                          Para conceder permissão: 1. Clique em \"Abrir configurações do sistema\" abaixo 2. Clique no botão + 3. Navegue até o aplicativo mostrado no Finder 4. Reinicie o Pindrop após conceder permissão Sem essa permissão, o texto só será copiado para sua área de transferência.             \"\""
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\" Pindrop necessita dell'autorizzazione di accessibilità per inserire testo in corrispondenza del cursore.                          Per concedere l'autorizzazione: 1. Fai clic su \"Apri Impostazioni di sistema\" di seguito 2. Fai clic sul pulsante + 3. Passa all'app mostrata nel Finder 4. Riavvia Pindrop dopo aver concesso l'autorizzazione Senza questa autorizzazione, il testo verrà solo copiato negli appunti.             \"\""
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "\"\"             The model failed to load within 60 seconds. This usually means the model files are corrupted or incompatible.                          To fix this:             1. Open Settings → Models             2. Delete the problematic model             3. Re-download the model                          If the problem persists, try a smaller model (Tiny or Base).             \"\"": {
      "extractionState": "stale",
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"             Das Modell konnte nicht innerhalb von 60 Sekunden geladen werden. Dies bedeutet normalerweise, dass die Modelldateien beschädigt oder inkompatibel sind.                          So beheben Sie das:             1. Öffnen Sie Einstellungen → Modelle             2. Löschen Sie das problematische Modell             3. Laden Sie das Modell erneut herunter                          Wenn das Problem weiterhin besteht, versuchen Sie ein kleineres Modell (Tiny oder Base).             \"\""
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"             The model failed to load within 60 seconds. This usually means the model files are corrupted or incompatible.                          To fix this:             1. Open Settings → Models             2. Delete the problematic model             3. Re-download the model                          If the problem persists, try a smaller model (Tiny or Base).             \"\""
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"             The model failed to load within 60 seconds. This usually means the model files are corrupted or incompatible.                          To fix this:             1. Open Settings → Models             2. Delete the problematic model             3. Re-download the model                          If the problem persists, try a smaller model (Tiny or Base).             \"\""
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"             Le modèle n'a pas pu se charger dans les 60 secondes. Cela signifie généralement que les fichiers du modèle sont corrompus ou incompatibles.                          Pour corriger cela :             1. Ouvrez Paramètres → Modèles             2. Supprimez le modèle problématique             3. Téléchargez à nouveau le modèle                          Si le problème persiste, essayez un modèle plus petit (Tiny ou Base).             \"\""
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\" モデルは 60 秒以内にロードできませんでした。これは通常、モデル ファイルが破損しているか、互換性がないことを意味します。                          これを修正するには: 1. [設定] → [モデル] を開きます。 2. 問題のあるモデルを削除します。 3. モデルを再ダウンロードします。 問題が解決しない場合は、より小さいモデル (Tiny または Base) を試してください。             「」"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\"             模型在 60 秒内未能加载。这通常意味着模型文件已损坏或不兼容。                          解决方法：             1. 打开设置 → 模型             2. 删除有问题的模型             3. 重新下载模型                          如果问题仍然存在，请尝试使用较小的模型（Tiny 或 Base）。             \"\""
          }
        },
        "pt-BR": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\" O modelo não foi carregado em 60 segundos. Isso geralmente significa que os arquivos do modelo estão corrompidos ou incompatíveis.                          Para corrigir isso: 1. Abra Configurações → Modelos 2. Exclua o modelo problemático 3. Baixe novamente o modelo Se o problema persistir, tente um modelo menor (Tiny ou Base).             \"\""
          }
        },
        "it": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"\" Impossibile caricare il modello entro 60 secondi. Questo di solito significa che i file del modello sono danneggiati o incompatibili.                          Per risolvere questo problema: 1. Apri Impostazioni → Modelli 2. Elimina il modello problematico 3. Scarica nuovamente il modello Se il problema persiste, prova un modello più piccolo (Tiny o Base).             \"\""
          }
        }
      }
    },
